==繁殖==
[[豆娘|豆娘]]交配时雄虫与雌虫形成一个「轮」(wheel)
<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marylandbiodiversity.com/view/27|title=American Rubyspot Hetaerina americana (Fabricius, 1798)|publisher=Maryland Biodiversity Project}}</ref>。 

雄虫会将雌虫体内过往交尾时留下的精子除清
<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.colorado.edu/asmagazine/2019/01/11/brilliant-coloration-american-rubyspots-signals-male-quality|title=If natural selection favors males with large pigment spots, why is the brilliant pigment limited to the base of the wings?|publisher=University of Colorado Boulder|website=Colorado Arts and Sciences Magazine|date=2019-01-11}}</ref>。  
